</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=13968\">Automated Tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=14472\">Pattern Matching -- Avoiding Hand-Tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=17373\">King Safety</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 22, 1998</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stuart_Cracraft&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=379136\">MTD(f)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 26, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=379495\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Enhanced_Transposition_Cutoff\" title=\"Enhanced Transposition Cutoff\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=381756\">Delta Pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selfli